NEWS/ChangeLog for hydroTSM
--------------------------

0.2-2-1   (under development)
    o 'fdc' and 'fdcu': New argument 'yat', for setting the position of the 'y' axis labels.
    o All the 'print' calls used to display information messages were replaced by a call to the 'message' function.

0.2-1   30-Nov-2010

    o R functions were split up into individual files.
    o 'dip', 'mip', 'yip': added error checking for the argument 'out.type'
    o 'drawxaxis': new argument: 'lab.fmt', for specifying the format of the axis' labels
    o 'hydroplot', 'sname2plot': removed argument 'sname', and new arguments: 'lab.fmt', 'xlab', 'ylab', 'col', 'cex', 'cex.main', 'cex.axis', 'cex.lab', 'lty', 'lwd', '...'
    o 'sname2ts'  : New arguments: 'from', 'to', 'date.fmt'
    o 'fdc' and 'fdcu': New arguments: 'cex.axis', 'cex.lab'



